snippet.title: Cramped Room of Death Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
**Updated trailer can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uQUAYWDQfBw

A teaser for my upcoming puzzling dungeon crawler where your weapon hinder you.

Wishlist now to play free beta when it's released https://store.steampowered.com/app/1389200/Cramped_Room_of_Death/

Or try out the demo here! https://hafizmrozlan.itch.io/cramped-room-of-death
